Summary: Small white objects above Offutt AFB Nebraska.
trends: There have been 6 other sightings in Bellevue
There were no other sightings in Bellevue on or around July 6th 2003
divs: Sighting Details On or about 07-06-2003,I was taking photos in the area of Offutt AFB Nebraska.I was phtographing the RC-135 aircraft that were flying in the area. Iphotographed a RC-135 cobra ball aircraft that was taking off out of the westside of the base.Days later after I got the photos developed, there is an image of an objectalong with the RC-135. In the photograph you can see the RC-135 in the lowerleft of the photo. In the uppper left there is a unknowen object. The objectappears to have a white upper section and a lower section that appears black ordark black.As I took the photo, the RC-135 was the only aircraft in my camera viewfinder.I noticed the object only after the photos were developed.
